*state
-state me hum component ka data store karne ke liye use hota hai
-state ki value hum directly nai change kar sakte
-state ki value ko change karne ke liye hame SET method milti hai
-state me hum initial value pass kar sakte hai useState(0)


*useEffect
-react ke under sideeffect ko control karne ke liye use karte hai
-eg app koi website me peheli bar aaye toh api call karne ke liye or data lane ke liye
-koi state or props ke value change hone par kuch check/operation karna ho
-there are three type
    -first time call 
    -first time + every time
    -with dependency
- in dependency we can pass state and props 
dependency type -1 blanck array dependency ,2 with dependency and 3 with out dependency

-without dependency [] useEffect call always
-with dependency blanck array [] call once a time
- and with dependency call when state and props change base on state and props
